      • ScriptProcessor

        public ScriptProcessor()
        Default constructor for deserialization.

      • ScriptProcessor

        public ScriptProcessor​(String language,
                       String name,
                       Object... args)
        Create a ScriptProcessor that wraps a script written in the specified language and identified by the specified name. The specified args will be passed during execution of the script.
        Parameters:
        language - the language the script is written. Currently, only "js" (for JavaScript) is supported
        name - the name of the InvocableMap.EntryProcessor that needs to be executed
        args - the arguments to be passed to the InvocableMap.EntryProcessor

    • Method Detail

      • process

        public R process​(InvocableMap.Entry<K,​V> entry)
        Description copied from interface: InvocableMap.EntryProcessor
        Process a Map.Entry object.

        Note: if this method throws an exception, all modifications to the supplied entry or any other entries retrieved via the BackingMapContext.getBackingMapEntry(java.lang.Object) API will be rolled back leaving all underlying values unchanged.

        Specified by:
        process in interface InvocableMap.EntryProcessor<K,​V,​R>
        Parameters:
        entry - the Entry to process
        Returns:
        the result of the processing, if any
